# Forge Council architecture

- Control plane: modular monolith; **runners isolated** (local / self-hosted / cloud).
- Orchestration follows explicit **state machine** in `ARCHITECTURE.md`; persist transitions + ledger events, not chat.
- Integration plane: model adapters, MCP, git, CI, filesystem — all **policy-scoped**.
- Storage: relational workflow state, object artifacts, vector retrieval, append-only ledger — see `DATA_MODEL.md`.

When changing structure, update `ARCHITECTURE.md` and relevant JSON Schemas under `schemas/forge_council/v1/`.
